Rothwell Market Dataset Summary
The Rothwell Market dataset captures comprehensive information about the vendors, products, customer reviews, and vendor nominations within the market. The dataset is designed to support the development of a digital solution for managing vendor information, product details, customer feedback, and vendor recognition.
